Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.87,0:01:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙中最長的一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.21,0:01:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在就任命泰勒少校為特別指揮官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.42,0:01:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位!宿敵拉爾康\N很愚笨的突破最終防衛線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.32,0:01:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而向我們發動總攻擊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.09,0:01:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是不必恐慌!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.83,0:01:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們上層已經把全軍指揮權
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.43,0:01:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交給精通敵人旗艦\N梅爾巴號的泰勒全責指揮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.94,0:01:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泰勒艦長宣言絕不會輸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.57,0:02:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為輔佐經驗尚淺的艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.28,0:02:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和三船中將也要\N搭乘驅逐艦微風號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.61,0:02:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許有很多人對泰勒艦長的\N指揮能力抱有疑問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.62,0:02:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請不用擔心!盡情的戰吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.06,0:02:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要怕死!去取勝利吧!\N這就是我的命令!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.80,0:02:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泰勒…能保持這樣的臉孔\N只是現在而已呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.57,0:02:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼?\N那是真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.31,0:02:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會錯的,依據報告敵人的指揮官\N是以前我們抓來作俘虜的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.98,0:02:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那位傑斯迪．植木．泰勒\N已經證明了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.65,0:02:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.18,0:02:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…那位泰勒?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.29,0:02:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這場戰爭如果得到勝利的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.96,0:02:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,力勸戰爭的我信用就會提高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.00,0:02:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果打敗\N就把責任推在皇帝身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.00,0:03:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,皇帝的權力就會衰弱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.00,0:03:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼樣\N最後笑的人就是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.17,0:03:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有想到那個八哥八哥\N會成為敵人指揮官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.67,0:03:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼,特姆?\N為什麼志願作指揮官呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.21,0:03:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不說話?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.55,0:03:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特姆,聽不懂我的話嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.72,0:03:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫非,你想殺掉八哥八哥嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.26,0:04:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快答覆呀,特姆\N不答覆的話就不准許你的要求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.07,0:04:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不回答?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.37,0:04:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陛下,我是為了陛下\N為了我們帝國…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.01,0:04:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想討伐泰勒!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.35,0:04:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要把八哥八哥…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.75,0:04:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長不見了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.36,0:04:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有去參加會議\N也沒有在房間裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.42,0:04:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不在這裡,這樣的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.09,0:04:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫非承受不了\N當指揮官的強大壓力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.43,0:04:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跑到什麼地方躲起來了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.83,0:04:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不可能這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.38,0:04:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各加速器正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.12,0:04:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,動力引擎燃燒室正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.45,0:05:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,液體氧氣桶正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.79,0:05:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電氣、油壓自動系統正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.82,0:05:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手控和自動切換機能正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.79,0:05:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以上各部門都正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.80,0:05:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳們兩位都進去駕駛艙裡\N作最後的檢查吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.10,0:05:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是,我們知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.37,0:05:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,艦長!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.11,0:05:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒有戰鬥啦\N好好的來幹一場吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.42,0:05:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.16,0:05:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備好放著\N要維持永遠可以使用的狀態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.16,0:05:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託妳了,春美小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.17,0:05:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.77,0:05:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦?艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.81,0:05:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們久等了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.84,0:06:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長!\N你去哪裡呀?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.45,0:06:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒去參加作戰會議嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.85,0:06:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.85,0:06:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我來看一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.12,0:06:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.86,0:06:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發現敵人艦隊!捕捉到好像是\N敵人超龐大戰艦的影像!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.87,0:06:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泰勒艦長怎麼啦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.87,0:06:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡,這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.20,0:06:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙!\N把作戰會議當成什麼呀!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.21,0:06:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想玩弄我們嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.14,0:06:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡的話,我怎麼會玩弄你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.21,0:06:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無謂的擔心對身體不好喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.81,0:06:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切事情就交由我泰勒\N來處理好啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.22,0:06:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,靜下來!\N大家靜下來!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.23,0:06:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身為拉爾康帝國\N戈撒十六世告訴各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.56,0:06:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始\N以巡洋艦特羅梅作旗艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.07,0:06:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同時派任艦長魯巴拉巴特姆\N為全艦隊的總指揮官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.24,0:07:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陛下,請稍等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.04,0:07:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.91,0:07:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可…可是…!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.91,0:07:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行!事情已經決定了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.91,0:07:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特姆!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.85,0:07:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.92,0:07:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.24,0:07:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,旗艦梅爾巴和護衛艦隊\N留在這個地方待命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.61,0:07:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他的艦隊就跟著\N這艘特羅梅號航行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.58,0:08:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,航空母艦鳳鸚號\N和護衛艦隊留下之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.32,0:08:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他艦隊出發!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.28,0:08:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,航空母艦鳳鸚號\N和護衛艦隊留下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.99,0:08:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他艦隊出發!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.60,0:08:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陛下待在這個地方\N如果萬一有危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.97,0:08:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先避難到防護室吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.68,0:08:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不,在這裡就可以\N我想看清楚一切事情的經過情形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.98,0:08:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.01,0:08:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣就用妳的眼睛去看吧\N看我旺克得到新力量時的一瞬間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.52,0:09:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到戰鬥區域1500
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.87,0:09:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不久之後就要衝入\N和敵人艦隊戰鬥的區域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.04,0:09:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全艦成紡錘陣形,全速前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.71,0:09:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通知全艦,馬上…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.74,0:09:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全艦,全速前進!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.68,0:09:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要衝入戰鬥區域了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.72,0:09:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特姆大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.10,0:10:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衝入戰鬥區域裡面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.37,0:10:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泰勒艦長!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.04,0:10:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的指示怎麼啦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.44,0:10:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦…艦長!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.11,0:10:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害怕了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.74,0:10:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該不會忘了你說過\N絕對不會輸這句話吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.11,0:10:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 艦長!\N- 快下下一個命令!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.65,0:10:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特姆大人,請快下下一個命令!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.12,0:10:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全艦繼續前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.76,0:10:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼樣,前進!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.46,0:10:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.96,0:10:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打…打算做什麼呀?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.08,0:11:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長,再接近就會有危險啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.11,0:11:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泰…泰勒\N你這傢伙怎麼啦攻擊命令呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.52,0:11:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泰勒!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.52,0:11:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦…艦長!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.19,0:11:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼不說話呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.19,0:11:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特姆大人,攻擊命令!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.20,0:11:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特姆大人!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.80,0:11:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要等待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.84,0:12:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長,快下攻擊命令!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.87,0:12:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.84,0:12:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙!沒有辦法的話\N現在就在這裡放棄指揮權吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.55,0:12:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三船中將大人說得對!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.51,0:12:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通知全艦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.22,0:12:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.22,0:12:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣繼續前進!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.57,0:12:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特姆大人,還要等待嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.80,0:13:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個光線是什麼呀?\N究竟是怎麼一回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.94,0:13:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,集中了這麼多的船艦\N每一船艘都帶有電能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.11,0:13:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經成飽和狀態了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.28,0:13:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飽和狀態?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.86,0:13:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泰勒…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.93,0:14:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快下攻擊命令吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.67,0:14:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太早!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.30,0:14:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特姆大人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.64,0:14:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希哈斯,妳看不出他的手法嗎?\N還太早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.01,0:14:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的手法?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.61,0:14:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的,這是計謀\N是那個泰勒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.35,0:14:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦…艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.99,0:15:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長究竟在想什麼呀?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.68,0:15:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泰勒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.08,0:16:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦…艦長笑了,莫非…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.82,0:16:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們久等了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.75,0:16:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個笑臉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.46,0:16:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們久等了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.12,0:16:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是那時候的笑臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.06,0:16:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種從容不迫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.07,0:16:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三船中將閣下!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.81,0:16:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放開!放開!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.48,0:16:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請冷靜,中將大人!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.12,0:16:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不得打擾艦長的工作!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.83,0:16:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看不出來…!\N他的本意看不出來!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.50,0:16:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泰勒…!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.47,0:16:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 特姆大人?\N- 囉嗦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.47,0:16:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.93,0:18:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.60,0:18:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特姆大人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.24,0:18:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泰勒…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.64,0:19:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.24,0:19:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.34,0:19:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.68,0:19:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.01,0:19:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.02,0:20:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喉嚨乾的要死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.69,0:20:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長,請振作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.02,0:20:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.37,0:20:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長,有電報給艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.37,0:20:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電報?請唸一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.38,0:20:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是,惑星聯合宇宙軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.41,0:20:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和拉爾康帝國軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.71,0:20:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭賀你們兩軍的勝利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.05,0:20:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前惑星聯合宇宙軍提督\N羅培魯特．J．哈奈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.65,0:20:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是哈奈提督打來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.06,0:20:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭賀兩軍勝利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.33,0:20:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是令人高興的賀詞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.40,0:20:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話提督們就會安心了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.73,0:20:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特姆…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.34,0:20:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.20,0:20:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好在那個時候我有相信你的話\N真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.65,0:21:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?\N為什麼,特姆!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.38,0:21:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陛下,我並非為了單單要討伐\N泰勒而志願擔任指揮官的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.66,0:21:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.69,0:21:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信泰勒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.43,0:21:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個傢伙如果正如我所想的\N是男子漢的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.26,0:21:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是真正的指揮官的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.40,0:21:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這場戰爭就不必流血吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.77,0:21:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來八哥八哥\N正是你所想像的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.44,0:21:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…\N其實我也頭一次經驗到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.78,0:21:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,士兵們所感受到的恐懼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.45,0:21:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然,泰勒並不是普通的人
